3FDFED6E.Line5.123EBF: Someone must separate her from that accursed axe! The town militia won't stand a chance.

675C43AC.Line3.123EBF: Her face was pained, as if she could not stop herself. The axe... it seemed to feed on the blood...

8ED899EA.Line1.123EBF: A madwoman with an axe! She massacred my knights, like they were children...
